ack.title: Acknowledgments
ack.p: The authors are grateful to Professor J.E. Moreton from University of Maryland for providing language help and would like to acknowledge the Division of Entomology, National Institute of Health of Thailand, Department of Medical Sciences, Thailand, for their supply of the gravid female Ae. aegypti mosquitoes.
